</ol><blockquote><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">本文主要编译自：</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2020/07/dogs-may-use-earth-s-magnetic-field-take-shortcuts">Dogs may use Earth’s magnetic field to take shortcuts</a></span></p></blockquote>
